    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>James Fairbairn Smith was editor-in-chief of <title render="italic">Masonic World</title> and a writer on the history of masonry.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The James Fairbairn Smith collection include correspondence, research files, and manuscripts of his writings.</p>
    </scopecontent>
